E4Plus1.uk.description: Theresa risks her own safety to help Mercedes. Darren extends an olive branch to Tony. Cleo gets some bittersweet news. A resident opens up about abuse. And Lucas spirals out of control... [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Darren extends an olive branch to Tony. Cleo receives some bittersweet news. And a resident opens up about recent abuse.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: All eyes are on Lucas as his desperate bid to win back Dillon begins to spiral out of control. Frankie confides in Dodger, but will his concern make her question her new beau?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister, Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sports of the lawnmower, motorbike and bicycle variety.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Black Pearl: A struggling seafood restaurant in Manhattan, The Black Pearl, is hampered by debts, kitchen problems and three owners who all want to run things their way. (S2 Ep7) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Fiesta Sunrise: A cockroach-infested kitchen means that the customers have to leave for their own safety at Fiesta Sunrise, a Mexican restaurant in West Nyack. (S2 Ep9) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pygmoelian: After he's snubbed for a Duff beer calendar, Moe goes for plastic surgery and ends up so handsome that he becomes a soap star. (S11 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart to the Future: Bart foresees his adult future as a struggling rock guitarist crashing on Ralph Wiggum's couch, while Lisa becomes President. (S11 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Days of Wine and D'Oh'ses: After forgetting his birthday party, Barney quits drinking and takes helicopter flying lessons. (S11 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pilot: The first ever episode of the hit sitcom. Leonard and Sheldon's geeky world is shaken up by the arrival of a beautiful new neighbour. (S1 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Big Bran Hypothesis: Sheldon sneaks into Penny's flat to tidy it. She's not happy about it. (S1 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fuzzyboots Corollary: Leonard is upset when he discovers that Penny is seeing someone, so he plucks up the courage to ask a woman out on a date. (S1 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Luminous Fish Effect: Getting fired forces Sheldon to ponder life outside physics, so Leonard has to take drastic action to snap his friend out of his reverie. (S1 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hamburger Postulate: Leonard thinks he's been wasting his time on Penny, so he turns his attention to Leslie. Sheldon's uncomfortable with a change to his hamburger routine. (S1 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Middle Earth Paradigm: Penny's Halloween party puts Leonard, Sheldon, Howard and Raj through a demanding new test of their social skills. (S1 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Dumpling Paradox: When Howard seduces Penny's friend and spends the night with her in Penny's flat, Penny asks if she can sleep on Leonard and Sheldon's sofa. (S1 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Grasshopper Experiment: Raj panics when his parents arrange a blind date for him. But he discovers that he can talk to her - after a few drinks. (S1 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cooper-Hofstadter Polarization: Sheldon and Leonard fall out when they're asked to collaborate at a physics conference. Penny tries to help but just makes things worse. (S1 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Loobenfeld Decay: Leonard and Sheldon each tell a lie to avoid going to see Penny singing on stage in a production of Rent, but Sheldon's fib gets out of control. (S1 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Pancake Batter Anomaly: Penny volunteers to nurse Sheldon when he's sick. But his friends, who know how miserable he is when he's ill, stay well away. (S1 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Jerusalem Duality: Sheldon's confidence is shaken to the core by a 15-year-old physicist who is clearly much brighter than him. (S1 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bat Jar Conjecture: Sheldon is ousted from the gang's Physics Bowl quiz team, so he decides to prove his superiority by forming his own team for the event. (S1 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Nerdvana Annihilation: When Penny makes fun of Leonard's habit of collecting goofy memorabilia, his friends kick up a fuss and try to keep him on the side of the nerds. (S1 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Shiksa Indeterminacy: Leonard, Raj and Howard all fall heavily for Sheldon's twin sister, but when Leonard comes up with a plan to win her heart, it's derailed by Sheldon. (S1 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Peanut Reaction: Penny throws a surprise party for Leonard, with help from Howard and Raj, but Sheldon's indulgence in an electronics shop throws her off track. (S1 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tangerine Factor: When Penny breaks up with her boyfriend, Leonard plucks up the courage to ask her out. And each of them turns to Sheldon for advice about their date. (S1 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: The walls close in on Mercedes as she races to get the money for her blackmailer. And Dillon and Rex try to support Ste as he struggles with his emotions.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer's Barbershop Quartet: Homer reminisces about the Be Sharps, the barbershop quartet he was in with Barney, Apu and Principal Skinner. Guest starring George Harrison. (S5 Ep1/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great Celebrity Bake Off...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...for Stand Up To Cancer: Matt Lucas dons an apron to bake alongside Annie Mac, Ed Gamble and Example, as they make cakes that depict what they did before they were famous.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: What do Britain's favourite telly watchers think of Strictly Come Dancing, Educating Yorkshire, The Girlfriend, Dragons' Den, Below Deck and Only Connect? (S26 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Dating Naked UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Double Trouble: Another naked newbie arrives, creating a huge test for one couple. And with the daters feeling vulnerable, there's a jaw-dropping double dumping. (S1 Ep6)
